@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dwgbxb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v0 = (v1 / (0.25 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.98)))
    tmp = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.84 / v0 + 0.86) - v1))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.17)) * v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(0.34)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.58)) / wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.39)))
    data[tid] = v0
